entry.title: xerrors/Yuxi-Know
entry.summary: 基于智能体 RAG 知识库的知识图谱问答系统。Langgraph + VueJS + Flask + Neo4j。大模型适配 OpenAI、Ollama、vLLM、国内主流大模型平台的模型调用。支持推理模型DeepSeek-R1、联网检索、工具调用。

entry.title: moeru-ai/airi
entry.summary: 💖🧸 A container of souls of AI waifu / virtual characters to bring them into our worlds, wishing to achieve Neuro-sama's altitude, completely LLM and AI driven, capable of realtime voice chat, Minecraft playing, Factorio playing. Can be run in Browser or Desktop.

entry.title: Moonofweisheng/wot-design-uni
